g.desc: ASVG scales to the size of the container provided on the web ...
g.text: ASVG scales to the size of the container provided on the web page. However, the following recommendations would give good results when using Visio to create SVG images.Recommend using metric page layout – A3 size and minimum Arial 12pt font sizes.There are 4 display sizes that can be configured:Large – recommend 430mm widthMedium – 290mmSmall – 160mmTiny – 80mm
